#url /records
#type operation
#method get
#description This operation retrieves descriptive metadata for each dataset included in the DH ATLAS knowledge graph. 

The fields returned by this operation are:

* *dataset*: the URI of the dataset
* *names*: the title(s) of the dataset
* *descriptions*: textual descriptions of the dataset
* *creators*: individuals or organizations responsible for creating the dataset
* *contributors*: entities that contributed to the dataset
* *publishers*: entities that published the dataset
* *languages*: the language(s) in which the dataset is available
* *educationalUses*: intended educational uses of the dataset
* *distributions*: links or references to the dataset's distribution formats
* *urls*: web addresses associated with the dataset
* *producers*: entities that produced the dataset
* *additionalType*: a more specific type or classification of the dataset
* *datePublished*: the publication date of the dataset
* *conditionsOfAccess*: information about access conditions or restrictions

Multiple values for each field are concatenated using " || " as a separator. 

#call /records
